---
title: Mexican Kumara & Feta Bowl with Chunky Guac & Corn Salsa
description: Get ready to be bowled over by this bright, bold and saucy combination of flavours. With roasted veg, a charred corn salsa, chunky smashed avocado and topped off with an oozy egg, this is a colourful taste of Mexico in an easy-to-eat, but hard-to-put down package!
